  <h1>The Arbour Report</h1>
  <p class="arbour-meta">Commission of Inquiry into Certain Events at the Prison for Women in Kingston<br>
  The Honourable Louise Arbour, Commissioner &mdash; 1996</p>

  <p>In April 1995, Justice Louise Arbour was appointed to investigate incidents at the Prison for Women in Kingston, Ontario, beginning April 22, 1994. Her report, submitted in 1996, became a landmark document in Canadian prison law and women's corrections.</p>

